  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this observational study, all enrolled patients having a thoracic surgical procedure
      requiring lung isolation will have a bispectral index (BIS) monitor placed at time of
      induction. BIS monitors are used to assist in determining depth of anesthesia. This study
      will evaluate changes in BIS before, during and after lung isolation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
